=head1 NAME

EXTENDED_SOURCE - For reducing extended source observations 

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Produces a coadded, sky-subtracted datacube from a group of SKY-OBJECT
pairs of IFU frames. Adapted from the spectroscopy recipe of the same name, 
and uses spectroscopy primitives.

=head1 AUTHOR

Paul Hirst <p.hirst@jach.hawaii.edu>
Stephen Todd <spt@roe.ac.uk>

=head1 COPYRIGHT

Copyright (C) 1998-2001 Particle Physics and Astronomy Research
Council. All Rights Reserved.

=cut

_REDUCE_SINGLE_FRAME_

_SPECTROSCOPY_MODE_
_PAIRWISE_GROUP_
_IFU_MODE_

_DIVIDE_BY_STANDARD_

_SPECTROSCOPY_MODE_
_FLUX_CALIBRATE_
_IFU_MODE_

_DELETE_TEMP_FILES_ KEEP=_scr,_cub
